==English==

===Pronunciation===
*:Rhymes: [[Rhymes:English:-ɪʃən|-ɪʃən]]

===Noun===
'''suspicion''' (''plural:'' '''[[suspicions]]''')

#The act of [[suspect]]ing something or someone, especially of something wrong.
#The condition of being suspected.
#[[Uncertainty]], [[doubt]].
#A [[trace]], or [[slight]] [[indication]].

